#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:1
msgid "Frontend Architecture"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:3
msgid ""
"The frontend is a React 19 TypeScript SPA built with Vite. It has no routing "
"library — navigation is a local state enum. It has no global state "
"management library — state lives in component hooks, with `localStorage` as "
"the only persistence layer."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:7
msgid "Project structure"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:9
msgid ""
"packages/frontend/src/\n"
"├── components/\n"
"│   ├── ChainBuilder/\n"
"│   │   ├── ChainBuilder.tsx       main orchestration component\n"
"│   │   ├── ChainComposer.tsx      drag-drop chain builder (dnd-kit)\n"
"│   │   ├── ChainConfig.tsx        configuration + execution panel\n"
"│   │   ├── ChainResults.tsx       execution results display\n"
"│   │   ├── DmnCard.tsx            individual DMN card\n"
"│   │   ├── DmnList.tsx            available DMNs panel\n"
"│   │   ├── ExecutionProgress.tsx  step-by-step progress indicator\n"
"│   │   ├── InputForm.tsx          dynamic input form generation\n"
"│   │   ├── ExportChain.tsx        export modal (JSON / BPMN 2.0)\n"
"│   │   ├── SemanticView.tsx       semantic analysis tab\n"
"│   │   ├── ValidationBadge.tsx    governance status badge\n"
"│   │   └── ValidationPanel.tsx    chain validation status display\n"
"│   ├── BpmnModeler/\n"
"│   │   ├── BpmnModeler.tsx        main orchestrator\n"
"│   │   ├── BpmnCanvas.tsx         bpmn-js canvas wrapper\n"
"│   │   ├── BpmnProperties.tsx     properties panel\n"
"│   │   ├── ProcessList.tsx        process management sidebar\n"
"│   │   └── DmnTemplateSelector.tsx DMN/DRD dropdown for BusinessRuleTask\n"
"│   ├── GraphView.tsx              D3.js RDF graph visualisation\n"
"│   ├── ResultsTable.tsx           SPARQL results table + CSV export\n"
"│   └── Changelog.tsx              version history display\n"
"├── services/\n"
"│   ├── sparqlService.ts           SPARQL query execution + result parsing\n"
"│   └── templateService.ts         localStorage CRUD for templates + "
"processes\n"
"├── utils/\n"
"│   ├── exportService.ts           JSON + BPMN 2.0 export logic\n"
"│   ├── exportFormats.ts           export format definitions\n"
"│   ├── bpmnTemplates.ts           default BPMN XML templates\n"
"│   └── constants.ts               sample queries, preset endpoints\n"
"├── types/\n"
"│   ├── index.ts                   core TypeScript interfaces\n"
"│   ├── chainBuilder.types.ts      chain builder specific types\n"
"│   └── export.types.ts            export types\n"
"├── changelog.json                 version history data (JSON)\n"
"└── tutorial.json                  in-app tutorial content"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:52
msgid "Key TypeScript interfaces"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:54
msgid "**DMN model:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:56
msgid ""
"interface DmnModel {\n"
"  id: string;\n"
"  identifier: string;\n"
"  title: string;\n"
"  description?: string;\n"
"  inputs: DmnVariable[];\n"
"  outputs: DmnVariable[];\n"
"  organisation?: string;\n"
"  // Governance metadata\n"
"  validationStatus?: 'validated' | 'in-review' | 'not-validated';\n"
"  validatedByName?: string;\n"
"  validatedAt?: string;\n"
"  validationNote?: string;\n"
"  // Vendor metadata\n"
"  vendorCount?: number;\n"
"  vendors?: VendorService[];\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"interface DmnVariable {\n"
"  id: string;\n"
"  identifier: string;\n"
"  title: string;\n"
"  type: 'Integer' | 'String' | 'Boolean' | 'Date' | 'Double';\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:83
msgid "**Chain template (localStorage schema):**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:85
msgid ""
"interface ChainTemplate {\n"
"  id: string;\n"
"  name: string;\n"
"  description?: string;\n"
"  endpoint: string;\n"
"  chain: string[];         // ordered DMN identifiers\n"
"  testData?: Record<string, unknown>;\n"
"  type: 'sequential' | 'drd';\n"
"  // DRD-specific\n"
"  isDrd?: boolean;\n"
"  drdDeploymentId?: string;\n"
"  drdEntryPointId?: string;\n"
"  drdOriginalChain?: string[];\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:104
msgid "Drag-and-drop (dnd-kit)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:106
msgid ""
"The Chain Composer uses `@dnd-kit/core` for drag detection and `@dnd-kit/"
"sortable` for reordering within the composer. DMN cards in the Available "
"DMNs list are `Draggable`; the Chain Composer area is a `Droppable`. Cards "
"already in the composer use `SortableContext` for reordering."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:110
msgid "SPARQL service"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:112
msgid ""
"`sparqlService.ts` handles query execution via the backend proxy endpoint (`/"
"v1/triplydb/query`). For direct SPARQL endpoints in development, it includes "
"a CORS fallback. Result parsing handles both standard `application/sparql-"
"results+json` and variations in binding formats."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:116
msgid "Template service (localStorage)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:118
msgid ""
"`templateService.ts` provides the localStorage interface for both chain "
"templates and BPMN processes. All storage keys are prefixed with `linkeddata-"
"explorer-`. Templates are namespaced by endpoint URL so switching endpoints "
"does not surface templates from another dataset."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:120
msgid "Key functions:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:122
msgid ""
"getUserTemplates(endpoint: string): ChainTemplate[]\n"
"saveTemplate(endpoint: string, template: ChainTemplate): void\n"
"deleteTemplate(endpoint: string, templateId: string): void\n"
"getBpmnProcesses(): BpmnProcess[]\n"
"saveBpmnProcess(process: BpmnProcess): void"
msgstr ""

